Flight readiness review for STS-132 underway today. The current target date for launch of NanoRacks and Kentucky Space hardware is May 14.
In other news, the managing partner for NanoRacks, Jeffrey Manber, recently participated
with the "SciGuy" at the Houston Chronicle, Eric Berger. Give it a read.
As the Kentucky Space blog transitions to the new web site, you may want to use
to get the latest blog posts. The old feed URL will no longer be updating. Kentucky Space is also @KySpace on Twitter.
